Package src.util

Class ApplicantCsvMapper

java.lang.Object
src.util.ApplicantCsvMapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicantRepository
public class ApplicantCsvMapper extends Object implements ApplicantRepository
CSV Mapper utility that implements ApplicantRepository for loading, saving, updating, and checking existence of Applicant records. Handle the parsing and serialization of applicant data to and from CSV format.
